;W[rs]LB[or:1][pr:2][os:3][rr:4][sr:5][rs:6]C[Dia.2

Black's cut at 1 is probably the way most people would go about capturing White.  It seems like a sharp move but White can still live.  White will counter dansu at 2 and then enlarge his eye space wiht 4 and 6.  As we can see White is alive.\lang1042\f1\fs18
