;B[rs]LB[pr:1][or:2][qr:3][rr:4][rs:5]C[Dia.3 Correct / Right in the middle

We finally come to the vital point.  Play right smack dab in the middle and you'll hit the spot.  White must block at 2 and then Black can come out with 3.  White 4 is futile, Black 5 captures it.  If White plays 2 and 3 then Black will play there and capture he stones, so 2 and 3 are matbogi.
\lang1042\f1\fs18
